    "In the refining phase, the learning rate was adjusted to 5 × 10 -5.",
    "The dimension of the embeddings was standardized to 200 for all models.",
    "We employed the Adam optimizer with a learning rate of 1 × 10 -3 and applied early stopping by monitoring NDCG on the validation set.",
    "Evaluation Metrics.Our evaluation encompasses the overall, warm, and cold recommendation performance, adopting a widely adopted full-ranking evaluation approach [11,14].",
    "Specifically, we employ Recall@𝐾 and NDCG@𝐾 as our primary metrics, where 𝑘 = 20."
